def generate_cryptogram
  letters = 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz'
  random_letters = []
  (1..26).each do |i|
    index = letters.index(letters[0])
    while true
      random_letters << letters.sample(index)
      break unless letters.include?(index)
    end
  end

  letters.each_with_index do |letter, i|
    puts "#{letter}#{random_letters.sample}"
  end
end

def prime_numbers(n)
  primes = []
  (2..n).each do |num|
    is_prime = true
    (2..num-1).each do |i|

        break
      end
    end
    primes << num if is_prime
  end
  primes
end
